--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PROJECT AGGREGATION NOTICE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This repository serves as the central point (aggregator) for the Flood and 
Outage Risk Management System solution. It contains the following sub-modules, 
each distributed under its own license terms as detailed within their 
respective directories:

1. Web Application (./app)
   - Description: Next.js Frontend & Backend Logic.
   - License: Apache 2.0
   - Third-party Attributions: See ./app/NOTICE

2. AI Model Core (./models)
   - Description: Traffic/Flood detection logic (YOLO based).
   - License: Apache 2.0 (Contains AGPL-3.0 logic & CC BY 4.0 Datasets).
   - Third-party Attributions: See ./models/NOTICE

3. Communication Bridge (./bridge)
   - Description: Middleware/API Connector.
   - License: Apache 2.0
   - Third-party Attributions: See ./bridge/NOTICE

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BUILD & DISTRIBUTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This collective work is licensed under Apache 2.0. However, compiling and 
running the full system requires complying with the licenses of all included 
sub-modules, specifically the AGPL-3.0 terms residing in the 'models' module.
